snippet: The United States dominated play in its second World Cup qualifying match against Jamaica, but the team needed a free kick by Herculez Gomez in the second half to earn the victory.
abstract: United States men's soccer team dominates play in its second World Cup qualifying match against Jamaica, and earns a 1-0 victory.
lead_paragraph: The United States dominated play in its second World Cup qualifying match against Jamaica, but the team needed a free kick by Herculez Gomez in the second half to earn the victory.

headline.seo: U.S. Avenges Loss to Jamaica in World Cup Qualifying
headline.main: With Swift Kick, U.S. Picks Up Important Win
headline.print_headline: With One Swift Kick, U.S. Picks Up an Important Win
